            "title": "前中國女首富時隔12年再入市 斥1.6億買西半山天御4房 涉逾千萬豪宅稅",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"536\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/RK7BMUIdvMA8xHbL4n8RRQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUzNg--/https://media.zenfs.com/vi/28hse_com_210/d01838f91f8489ea3bff93ba80d9940d\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%89%8D%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%A5%B3%E9%A6%96%E5%AF%8C%E6%99%82%E9%9A%9412%E5%B9%B4%E5%86%8D%E5%85%A5%E5%B8%82-%E6%96%A51-6%E5%84%84%E8%B2%B7%E8%A5%BF%E5%8D%8A%E5%B1%B1%E5%A4%A9%E5%BE%A14%E6%88%BF-%E6%B6%89%E9%80%BE%E5%8D%83%E8%90%AC%E8%B1%AA%E5%AE%85%E7%A8%85-082437970.html",
